  Thanks to Ulf (yeti at debianforum.de)!

* Sony Ericsson K550i phone (USB ID 0fce:d069, /dev/ttyACM0)

* Option GX301 (USB ID: 0af0:7011, /dev/ttyHS1), a.k.a.
	  T-Mobile web'n'walk Card compact III
  Thanks to Ulf, too (yeti at debianforum.de)!

* Option GT 3G Quad UMTS/GPRS Card (USB ID 0af0:6300, /dev/ttyUSB2)
  Thanks to guennid at debianforum.de

